### Parameters

| Parameter | Description | Default |
|-----------|-------------|---------|
| `--prd-id` | PRD ID - supports multiple formats (see below) | Required* |
| `--swarm` | Swarm number (1-N) - implement all PRDs in a swarm sequentially (v4.1.0) | Optional* |
